     C                     ADD  1         RRN
     C                     ADD  1         @RRN
     C                     ADD  1         CTRX
      *EDIT FIELD
     C                     Z-ADDN2HAHZ    NUM6    60
     C                     MOVELNUM6      @HKHZ
     C                     MOVE N2HABB    @HKHZ
      *
     C                     MOVELN2TEHI    @TEHI
      *EDIT PAGE
